results.description:
*** PROGRAM ***

- 18.00 Entry and warm food

- 18.45 Talk 1: "How to build a React Native App" - During the live coding session we'll discuss about how to build a React TODO list component on iOS and Android.
How to persist information across application reloads with AsyncStorage and more also will be on focus.
The main goal is to gain an understanding of how to get started building Native applications with React. - by Carina Syemyerdzhyan

- 19.30 Break 

- 19:45 Talk 2: "Tooling" - by  Bjørn Wikkeling

- 20:30 Social drinks
results.name: Tech Talk about React Native and Tooling!!
